description:
Teodora Rumenova Andreeva, better known by her stage name Andrea, is a Bulgarian pop-folk singer, musician, songwriter, actress and video director.

She was also part of the famous group Sahara, together with the Romanian Grammy Awards nominated producer Costi, they created the song "I Wanna" in collaboration with Shaggy and Bob Sinclar. The track was her biggest worldwide hit and it was on the top charts of Belgium, Germany, Switzerland and many more.
Some of the greatest Romanian artists, such as Andreea Banica and Akcent, and the Serbian star Ceca have identified her as the most famous performer in her homeland.

One of the biggest hits in her career is the duo Probvai Se (feat. Azis). The song remains the biggest hit-duet in the career of both performers in Bulgaria.
Andrea has won over 30 awards worldwide.
Andrea has collaborations with Costi, Shaggy, Bob Sinclar, Mario Winans, Alek Sandar, MC Yankoo, Azis, Otilia, Mario Joy, Edward Maya, Cvija, Sergio.
